a the LN32D403''s USB port. An intuitive, user-friendly interface allows access to music or pictures via the remote.</p> <h5>SRS Audio Technology</h5> <p>SRS'' TheaterSound, available in new Samsung HDTVs, is an all-in-one audio suite that directly addresses the three most common consumer TV audio complaints--inconsistent volume levels, unintelligible vocals, and poor, dimension-less sound. SRS helps ensure you get great audio from the LN32D403''s two three-watt speakers.</p> <h5>Exceeds ENERGY STAR Standards</h5> <p>The LN32D403 exceeds the strict energy efficiency guidelines set by the EPA and US Department of Energy by up to 30%. That means you get lower utility costs, and a smaller carbon footprint.</p> <div class="break"></div> <h4>LN32D403 Select Specifications</h4> <table class="data" width="100%"> <tbody> <tr> <th colspan="2">Video</th> </tr> <tr> <td>Screen Size:</td> <td>31.5 Inches</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Display Type:</td> <td>LCD</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Resolution:</td> <td>720p HD</td> </tr> <tr> <th colspan="2"><strong>Inputs</strong></th> </tr> <tr> <td>HDMI:</td> <td>2 (version 1.4)</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Component Video (Y/PB/PR):</td> <td>1</td> </tr> <tr> <td>PC Input:</td> <td>0</td> </tr> <tr> <td>USB 2.0 Ports:</td> <td>1</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Component Audio Input:</td> <td>1</td> </tr> <tr> <td>PC Audio Input:</td> <td>0</td> </tr> <tr> <th colspan="2"><strong>Outputs</strong></th> </tr> <tr> <td>Digital Audio Output:</td> <td>1 (Rear)</td> </tr> <tr> <th colspan="2">Weight and Dimensions</th> </tr> <tr> <td>Dimensions (WxHxD):</td> <td>31.3 x 20.1 x 3.2 Inches (31.3 x 22.5 x 9.9 Inches With Stand)</td> </tr> <tr> <td>Weight:</td> <td>19 lbs. (23.9 lbs. with stand)</td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <h4>What''s in the Box</h4> <p>LN32D403 32-inch Class LCD HDTV, Stand, Remote Control, Documentation, AV/Component Adapter, AV Adapter</p> <!-- Begin LED/LCD Feature Comparison Table --> <div class="break"></div> <br /> <hr /> <br /> <h4>Samsung 2011 LED/LCD Featur